  <entry>
    <title>《灵飞经》临习记录三</title>
    <url>/2020/11/21/%E3%80%8A%E7%81%B5%E9%A3%9E%E7%BB%8F%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%B4%E4%B9%A0%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%89/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="11-20"><a href="#11-20" class="headerlink" title="11.20"></a>11.20</h2><p>飞字，下半部分靠左右的撇和弯钩做个支撑，注意里面的撇和竖钩起笔都在第一笔的横里面，第二个横整体靠下起笔。</p>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td style="background-image: url('https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/YvWaVFu8LcCgJSl.jpg')"></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/ndrxEy2vl3LjZ8T.jpg"  ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/OdzPGpqERSlQK15.jpg" ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/Lg3uTdmBJ6DSjt2.jpg" ></center></td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p>鸟字，横折钩出钩的时候把握好速度，太快容易变成方笔，太慢墨会聚集。</p>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td style="background-image: url('https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/kEODeVWwMdBZJ1z.jpg')"></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/LXMpfwkYBe41usT.jpg"  ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/HywEd6fiN2JrPKa.jpg" ></center></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/9ztfMVAYbTOaje5.jpg" ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/S7pfGvtzugrZk26.jpg" ></center></td>
    </tr>
</table>


<h2 id="11-21"><a href="#11-21" class="headerlink" title="11.21"></a>11.21</h2><p>出，左低右高，注意左边两个竖的起笔差异，右边两个点倾斜的角度也不同，上面的点角度大些。</p>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td style="background-image: url('https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/9iBEUjCGltQngOx.jpg')"></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/4gVmh6JjypTb5uI.jpg"  ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/PVeNOD7TgGzioEq.jpg" ></center></td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p>岳字，下面的山并不是左右相等的均衡，左边放右边收，靠点把重心拉回来。</p>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td style="background-image: url('https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/2ixtvWVYn1Z64oR.jpg')"></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/PRcnIuz7WJpCwBG.jpg"  ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/zu3BgxDtfbZshjc.jpg" ></center></td>
    </tr>
</table>


<p style="font-size:1.15em;text-align:right;">Supremum</br>2020.11.21</p>]]></content>
