  <entry>
    <title>《灵飞经》临习记录二</title>
    <url>/2020/11/21/%E3%80%8A%E7%81%B5%E9%A3%9E%E7%BB%8F%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%B4%E4%B9%A0%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%BA%8C/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="11-18"><a href="#11-18" class="headerlink" title="11.18"></a>11.18</h2><p>或字，注意最后一个撇起笔往右边靠一些，才能让整个字显得饱满。斜钩起笔的方笔还不是很习惯。</p>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td style="background-image: url('https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/yx6978bsBuazPG1.jpg')"></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/fV2IxQt6XSoM3WF.jpg" ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/r6gOcpEVCLxvWZf.jpg"  ></center></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/k3vYO5i8jzSQBlf.jpg" ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/mRxCvE13OWc8tgZ.jpg" ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/ZM2iWfkvxEbRU7a.jpg"  ></center></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/ta3kBLwunZ7CA8y.jpg" ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/J16yFzDUkfvKVIo.jpg"  ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/GMYwPiEp8ebHquB.jpg"  ></center></td>
    </tr>
</table>

<h2 id="11-19"><a href="#11-19" class="headerlink" title="11.19"></a>11.19</h2><p>乃字，横折弯钩把它拆分成横折和弯钩就比较好掌握弯钩的弧度了，先往右走，快要出钩的时候再拉回来。</p>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td style="background-image: url('https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/v7maPF3rXqAeIoC.jpg')"></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/IUseFV5NniOLaX3.jpg"  ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/T9HYboaF7qlkXJC.jpg" ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/9DmQ5jzFOHTd47M.jpg" ></center></td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p>陆字，左耳旁竖的弧度注意一下,右下角的土字竖画和右上的竖画是存在差异的。</p>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td style="background-image: url('https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/i5NVJAGSKWyTlDR.jpg')"></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/21/ho1E2yg8QNALamK.jpg"  ></center></td>
