  <entry>
    <title>《灵飞经》临习记录五</title>
    <url>/2020/11/24/%E3%80%8A%E7%81%B5%E9%A3%9E%E7%BB%8F%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%B4%E4%B9%A0%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%BA%94/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="11-24"><a href="#11-24" class="headerlink" title="11.24"></a>11.24</h2><p>爱字，感觉很考验用笔节奏，结构上注意的是，宝盖的钩要粗一些平衡字的中部，必的左边第一个点尽量往下放，给最后的捺笔留点空间。</p>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td style="background-image: url('https://i.loli.net/2020/11/24/bj9XoCmvpT4ODeG.jpg')"></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/24/oXDTaZVjWAd2qf3.jpg"></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/24/Nn5G2VLDexJowgH.jpg"></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/24/egf3RKhiSqkF9nH.jpg"></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/24/3DzREvbWVnSJmc4.jpg"></center></td>
    </tr>
</table>


<p>此，注意三个竖画和点直接间隙的均等。最后一笔在弯的时候，总喜欢提笔，这个坏习惯一定要改正。</p>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td style="background-image: url('https://i.loli.net/2020/11/24/2tlYRXwd9uSeOZr.jpg')"></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/24/nB2YhNpg71TmAqX.jpg" ></center></td>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/24/1oFvre2Cb7swJun.jpg" ></center></td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p>有空的话把这个重新临一遍，应该比半年前有长进了。</p>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td ><center><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/11/24/tv2qxKUwlGkZcVg.jpg"></center></td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p style="font-size:1.15em;text-align:right;">Supremum</br>2020.11.24</p>]]></content>
